fields.name: protocolID
fields.description: Protocol identifier, identifying the output protocol for this poll request. The following are valid protocol identifiers: 0: UBX protocol, 1: NMEA protocol, 2-255: Reserved

issues: Inconsistent JSON schema (uses message_class instead of class_id)
Flat payload structure instead of nested
Minor text formatting error in field description (missing commas between protocol identifiers)

adjudication.reasoning: The message UBX-CFG-INF-POLL is highly stable across all generations (M8, M9, F9). The core protocol definition (Class 0x06, ID 0x02, 1-byte U1 payload) is identical in every source. Most extractions followed a consistent nested JSON schema. Extraction 1 used a flattened schema and different key names, which are considered extraction-specific template variations rather than protocol variations. Extraction 8 had minor whitespace/punctuation omissions in the text description.
